      <title>新加坡的中国富豪减少了法拉利和价值 7.5 万美元的威士忌消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/singapore-china-s-ultra-rich-cut-flashy-spending-after-money-laundering-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新加坡的繁荣时期，威士忌经销商曼吉特吉尔 (Manjit Gill) 每天都会向他的富有的中国客户出售至少一瓶威士忌，这些客户有时会一次性花费高达 10 万新元（7.5 万美元）购买单一麦芽威士忌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/singapore-china-s-ultra-rich-cut-flashy-spending-after-money-laundering-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
