      <title>随着银行释放风险，GoldenTree 看到了 100 亿美元的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/goldentree-sees-10-billion-opportunity-as-banks-unload-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资产规模 550 亿美元的 GoldenTree Asset Management 创始人史蒂文·塔南鲍姆 (Steven Tananbaum) 表示，他的公司在与那些希望在监管加强的背景下减轻贷款风险的银行进行交易时发现了机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/goldentree-sees-10-billion-opportunity-as-banks-unload-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 17:09:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
